<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zgh" dir="ltr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Udfal n useɣ — Terroir.ma</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: 'Tifinagh', 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px;">
  <h1 style="color: #c62828;">Useɣ n tmuɣli yettwaflaḍ</h1>

  <p>Aselway,</p>

  <p>
    Nesselmed-ak belli tɣuri-nnek ɣef useɣ n tmuɣli-nnek ɣef usebter Terroir.ma
    <strong>ttwaflaḍ</strong> ɣef tiɣiri-a:
  </p>

  <table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin: 24px 0;">
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; background: #f5f5f5; font-weight: bold;">Isem n tmuɣli</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">{{cooperativeName}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; background: #f5f5f5; font-weight: bold;">Azemz n uflaḍ</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">{{rejectedAt}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; background: #f5f5f5; font-weight: bold;">Aɣbalu</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; color: #c62828;">{{reason}}</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <p style="margin-top: 32px; color: #666; font-size: 0.9em;">
    Iyawalen-a ttwaznen s wudem awurman seg usebter Terroir.ma.<br>
    Ur d-trarreḍ ɣef yiyawalen-a.
  </p>
